To defeat the Empire, you must capture Darth Vader, Emperor Palpatine, and the Emperor's home planet of Coruscant.  If you chose 'Headquarters Only Victory', you need only capture Coruscant. The Empire will quickly begin searching for Master Luke, President Mon Mothma and our headquarters. We must protect them if we are to succeed. Use the Objectives window from my right click menu to see how the campaign is progressing.